Robert C. Feenstra, Alan Heston, Marcel P. Timmer, And Haiyan Deng (2009) <a href="https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Alan_Heston/publication/24008774_Estimating_Real_Production_and_Expenditures_Across_Nations_A_Proposal_for_Improving_the_Penn_World_Tables/links/556c7b2a08aefcb861d7e00e.pdf">Estimating Real Production And Expenditures Across Nations: A Proposal For Improving The Penn World Tables</a>. The Review of Economics and Statistics, February 2009, 91(1): 201â€“212.

