 	<li><strong>Geographical coverage:</strong> Global â€“ by country</li>
 	<li><strong>Time span:</strong> Since 1950</li>
 	<li><strong>Available at:</strong>Â It is online <a href="http://www.conference-board.org/data/economydatabase/">here</a>.</li>
</ul>

